modules.description: This module generates functions for spatial transformations of user-defined abstract and record types that include `Scad_ml.Scad.t` and `Scad_ml.Vec3.t`. It supports operations like translation, scaling, rotation, and mirroring, while respecting annotations such as `[@scad.unit]` and `[@scad.ignore]` to control transformation behavior on specific fields or types. It is used to manipulate 3D models and geometric marks with precise control over their spatial properties.
